Dialogue: 10,0:00:59.46,0:01:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,No....
Dialogue: 10,0:01:03.55,0:01:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it. No...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:04.92,0:01:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:09.22,0:01:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:12.46,0:01:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:13.78,0:01:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Please... Stop!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:16.85,0:01:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:48.84,0:01:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Please...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:49.96,0:01:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:51.73,0:01:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Please...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:53.56,0:01:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:12.78,0:02:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What was that voice just now?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:14.86,0:02:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,A crow. Just a crow, Aria.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:17.64,0:02:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? It suddenly went “kaa,” \Nand it startled me.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:22.74,0:02:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right. I was totally moved.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:25.20,0:02:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,About what?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:26.81,0:02:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, being welcomed personally \Nby the principal. {that guy I assume}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:31.94,0:02:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,As it happens,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:33.57,0:02:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm bringing in all of this year's new students,\N including you, on this ship.{get rid of passive voice!}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:38.39,0:02:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, you are not only my students,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:41.50,0:02:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,but also precious cocoons destined to become treasures of the 21st-century classical music world. {/pupa}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:47.81,0:02:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Until the day you grow into beautiful, \Ntalented butterflies,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:53.24,0:02:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I will cherish you with the utmost care.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:57.24,0:03:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Is something wrong? Another crow?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:01.08,0:03:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,No, crows don't play the guitar.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:08.25,0:03:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I-Isogu! Did you come all this way for me? {non-standard name but idk what else it could be; isogu means "to hurry"}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:16.03,0:03:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{Ya-hoh; maybe Yoo-hoo!}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:17.27,0:03:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Aria's knight in shining armor, \Nher emotional support and sweetheart, {/beloved lover}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:20.64,0:03:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,a rock 'n' roller and hip-hop star,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:22.74,0:03:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,and also somehow, the national pole-vaulting champion, Isogu is here! {-chan}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:28.27,0:03:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And who exactly bestowed all these titles on you? You stalker{stalking creep}… {lit: how dare you make up all those things on your own }
Dialogue: 10,0:03:32.18,0:03:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that your boyfriend?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:34.28,0:03:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not! What are you saying?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:36.27,0:03:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,N-Not at all!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:38.18,0:03:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never seen or heard of such a vulgar man.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:42.41,0:03:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, good.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:44.29,0:03:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd better not doubt me! \NI really don't know him!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:47.60,0:03:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I could blow someone like that away with a single breath. Phew!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:50.29,0:03:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, what a cute little pout! \NAre you asking me for a kiss?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:54.92,0:03:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:59.80,0:04:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my, he really flew away.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:02.73,0:04:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And there wasn't even any wind.
Comment: 10,0:04:05.54,0:04:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:08.82,0:04:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,B-Breasts!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:10.81,0:04:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No, not exactly breasts... I mean, great boobs... \NAs in... very impressive building! {some pun where she gradually turns oppai into rippana, I don't quite understand it myself}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:15.89,0:04:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. That's a representative\N architectural style from my homeland.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:20.55,0:04:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? So that means that building is...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:24.76,0:04:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. That's where you'll be spending your days: \Nthe Royal Elegance Academy.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:30.67,0:04:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa… That sketchy building is the academy? {vulgar/crude}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:34.92,0:04:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It totally looks like boobs.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:40.14,0:04:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You are all super-elite prodigies \Nchosen from geniuses all over the world.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:49.85,0:04:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,After training rigorously here under me,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:52.94,0:04:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,you will become brilliant stars shining\N across the 21st-century classical music world.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:59.90,0:05:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:03.87,0:05:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinbi?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:07.12,0:05:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my younger sister, Shinbi.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:10.11,0:05:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll be teaching you alongside me.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:14.13,0:05:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Pleased to meet you.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:15.97,0:05:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Likewise.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:18.28,0:05:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Izumo Binan has arrived.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:20.18,0:05:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,B-Binan?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:22.66,0:05:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep! Binan as in “beautiful man.” {美男}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:27.91,0:05:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,A name reflects the person. \NThat's me in a nutshell.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:34.23,0:05:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be Principal Karma. \NSorry I'm late.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:36.97,0:05:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I was competing in a guitar contest in Italy.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:39.94,0:05:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Strange… I've heard of you, but this is an all-girls academy, except in special cases...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:46.98,0:05:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I {\i1}am{\i0} your special case.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:49.08,0:05:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:50.31,0:05:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already received permission \Nfrom the government. {lit: from the country}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:52.79,0:05:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,His father has made a very generous donation to our government.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:57.91,0:06:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I look forward to working with you.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:01.05,0:06:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Same to you all.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:02.43,0:06:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Izumo Binan, master of classical guitar \Nand a computer whiz.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:06.66,0:06:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard rumors you're a hacker.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:09.66,0:06:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's bad for the reputation. {disreputable; scandalous; disgraceful}{think he means "hacker sounds like some criminal"}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:11.39,0:06:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure we've already investigated your case \Nand declined your admission.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:16.28,0:06:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,However, your government overruled it. {approved}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:26.90,0:06:29.32,Thought,,0,0,0,,Oh? It happened again…
Dialogue: 10,0:06:29.32,0:06:33.55,Thought,,0,0,0,,Just when I was thinking, "I wish a thunderbolt \Nwould strike and end this already."
Dialogue: 10,0:06:33.55,0:06:34.60,Thought,,0,0,0,,Honestly… {/what in the}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:34.60,0:06:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you girls...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:37.51,0:06:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I asked you to tell me your names.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:41.42,0:06:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I'm Aria.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:44.23,0:06:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Yan.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:46.10,0:06:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Aria and Yan, nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:48.95,0:06:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And you are?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:51.24,0:06:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Luna, and this is my little sister, Monica.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:54.92,0:06:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you be {\i1}the{\i0} one who won first place \Nat that Italian guitar competition?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:59.69,0:07:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? You knew already?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:02.29,0:07:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'm now known as the world's number-one classical guitar prince.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:06.70,0:07:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Karen. \NYour guitar playing gave me chills.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:11.20,0:07:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course it did. \NMy guitar always hits you hard.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:15.89,0:07:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially down there.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:21.22,0:07:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Refrain from vulgar behavior!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:23.71,0:07:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed. To become a refined musician, \None must possess proper elegance.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:30.63,0:07:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You in particular were chosen \Nfrom billions of young people worldwide,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:35.16,0:07:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,handpicked by our government as future shining stars of the classical music world,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:40.48,0:07:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,and gathered here to be carefully nurtured:\Nthe cream of the crop. {super elite}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:44.69,0:07:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Any behavior that stains our nation's authority \Nor its artistic spirit will not be tolerated.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:52.41,0:07:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? So you're a master \Nof Chinese martial arts, Yan? {taikyoku ken = https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tai_chi}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:58.63,0:08:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't call myself a master, \Nbut when I went to Hong Kong, my grandfather...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:02.75,0:08:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I learned martial arts from my father too.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:05.84,0:08:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Is your dad a samurai? {maybe should keep that "aria's papa" to convey her foreign accent?}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:09.11,0:08:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a samurai. A ninja.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:11.76,0:08:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,A ninwhat?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:15.69,0:08:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, please... That joke was pretty hip, Yan. {ninja / nanja - dunno how to convey it in english; hip is probably "hip; trendy; cool; with it"}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:20.73,0:08:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,More or less. {??? probably something in chinese}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:22.13,0:08:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So, is your dad really a ninja?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:24.28,0:08:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, from the Gasshuin style, \Ndescended from the Yellow River lineage. {???? can't find any mention of it but idk what else it could be}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:28.61,0:08:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And your mom's a former Russian noble?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:32.30,0:08:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I hear.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:34.68,0:08:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,They even say she's a witch.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:38.38,0:08:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,A witch? No way.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:41.35,0:08:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I thought too: no way.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:43.92,0:08:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:45.40,0:08:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I-Isogu?!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:50.12,0:08:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, my cutie!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:52.92,0:08:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, what a clingy guy. I wish someone that annoying would just fly away!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:00.73,0:09:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa... I'm flying away!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:04.90,0:09:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh… He really did fly away.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:08.58,0:09:11.41,Thought,,0,0,0,,Could it be that I'm…
Comment: 10,0:09:18.58,0:09:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:19.88,0:09:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:22.05,0:09:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:23.28,0:09:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it. You were dazzled\N by how beautiful I am.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:27.23,0:09:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What are you talking about? No way!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:28.92,0:09:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Seeing how flustered you are,\N that must be it.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:31.94,0:09:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You've just decided that yourself! \NFirst of all, you...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:35.49,0:09:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Our country, Orgum, \Nmay only be a micronation in Europe,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:39.12,0:09:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,but by building this royal academy
Dialogue: 10,0:09:41.54,0:09:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and gathering talented youth \Nfrom around the world to educate them,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:45.59,0:09:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,we are undertaking a major cultural project.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:48.35,0:09:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Take pride in that.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:51.58,0:09:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're just here to fool around, \Nyou may leave at once.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:56.96,0:10:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Principal... I apologize.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:00.70,0:10:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as you understand.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:04.34,0:10:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be more careful too.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:11.10,0:10:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:14.22,0:10:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Karen, you'll receive a private lesson \Ntonight at 8 in the principal's room.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:21.15,0:10:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,A private lesson from the principal himself! \NI'm so honored.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:46.46,0:10:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:49.76,0:10:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,This guy tried to touch Aria's butt!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:53.89,0:10:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No, that's not it! There was something stuck there, so I was trying to remove it.
Comment: 10,0:10:57.80,0:10:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Comment: 10,0:10:58.77,0:10:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:00.51,0:11:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:01.87,0:11:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,"If you're feeling lonely, just look up"?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:06.82,0:11:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:08.54,0:11:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Isogu!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:10.02,0:11:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You can let him go!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:11.55,0:11:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Aria?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:13.95,0:11:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,See? You can let me go, Yan.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:15.73,0:11:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't call me so casually! {because yan-chan}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:21.47,0:11:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough already!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:25.23,0:11:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,This must be fate, Aria!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:27.80,0:11:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm always right behind you. {perevo and muzu frfr}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:29.95,0:11:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,If anything happens, just turn around.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:32.72,0:11:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, I'm starting to get a headache.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:36.08,0:11:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, look...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:37.54,0:11:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Huh? Where did you go, Isogu?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:39.64,0:11:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Ta-da! Told you I'm always right behind you.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:43.27,0:11:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez, don't scare me like that! \NWhat is your...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:47.27,0:11:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Wh-Where?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:49.63,0:11:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:51.49,0:11:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, behind me, right... huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:54.66,0:11:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this kid your boyfriend?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:56.63,0:11:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No! He's a stalker.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:59.62,0:12:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Then we'll make him leave.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:03.58,0:12:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:05.12,0:12:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. I won't be rough.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:07.98,0:12:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'll keep it a secret \Nfrom the principal too.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:12.06,0:12:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, that's so kind of you!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:26.23,0:12:28.44,Thought,,0,0,0,,A-Aren't you supposed to be a woman?
